Maintainer: Maxime Faymonville <faymonville@statistik.tu-dortmund.de>
Description: Flexible simulation of INAR data using a general pmf to define the innovations' distribution, semiparametric and parametric estimation of INAR models (including a small sample refinement for the semiparametric setting) and different procedures to appropriately bootstrap INAR data.
